http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Workshop-for-research-scholars/article14013091.ece

The School of Education of Rani Channamma University will organise a 10-day “Workshop on Research Methodology Course in Social Science” for research scholars with sponsorship from ICSSR, New Delhi, soon. Research scholars interested in taking part may send their applications to rcuschoolofeducation @gmail.com. For more details and application forms, visit rcub.ac.in. The last date for sending applications is January 25. Selected candidates will be intimated on January 30. The dates of the workshop would be announced soon.